message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CC. The paper focuses on a machine comprehension corpus and the evaluation of script knowledge, which falls under natural language processing and artificial intelligence (cs.CL, cs.AI). The analysis of the corpus and the performance of existing machine comprehension models also involve machine learning and computational linguistics (cs.LG, cs.IR). The collection process for the corpus may also involve crowd-sourcing and human-computer interaction (cs.CC).
